FootNote: The 2007 and 2010 the TSA Table 6 (Domestic Supply & Internal Tourism Consumption) was compiled based on  data from the Jamaica Tourist Board for Inbound Tourism Expenditure and  a Domestic Tourism Expenditure Survey. It must be noted that domestic tourism accounts for a small percentage of Tourism Direct GDP (3.9 per cent in 2019). Inbound tourism, which accounts for the majority of Tourism Direct GDP, is done for all years.
